{
  "stem": "26728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And even if in their beds, if they happened to be in the beds, there was just uh, stool, fecal matter, just all over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Like that-- the-- the combination of that smell plus this death smell was what was the hardest thing for me to cope with, sense wise.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The sensory data, what you could see, was just too much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Um, it was almost like it wasn't real.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was surreal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, I mean, you could see these dead people, and there were hundreds of them, hundreds of them, in this nice-- in these stacks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You could walk down a half football field length, on both sides would be these-- and the smell was there, of course, all the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And uh-- [PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that-- they-- the people that were still alive, were-- by the time I got there, were being cared for by the medics from the army.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And 50% of them were lost.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they were-- they were-- they were trying to-- First, first they were giving them penicillin, which of course was the cure-all for everything in those days, and sulfa drugs.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Trying to clean them all up, you know, as best they could with alcohol.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they also did-- they used DDT on everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All of us were dusted with DDT.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, we had-- all of us had to-- we had to have our-- our heads, our shirts, our inside of our trousers, inside of our shoes, and our boots.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My airplanes were dusted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they dusted everything because of the-- the typhus, which was in every camp that I was in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was, uh, a lot of typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there were parasites or fleas, um, that, um, spread typhus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three days, three and a half days, maybe.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
